電動機設計                               DESIGN OF ELECTRIC MOTORS


  	電動機為機電系統中主要之致動元件，舉凡在國防，民生及一般工業皆具有舉足輕重之地位。Electric motors are a key component in any sorts of mechatronic systems and
applications. There are many types of electric motors such as induction motors, DC motors, reluctance motors, etc. Among them, brushless permanent magnet motors are increasingly applied due to the rapid development of magnetic material and electronic technology. Therefore, this course will focus on brushless permanent magnet motors, whose design and analysis will be the focus of study.


課程教育目標 

A 培育學生具備進階之船舶或機電系統及相關科技的研究、創造與規劃能力。 Cultivate students to have the ability of advanced ship and mechatronic system with relative technology research, the ability of creativity and design.B 培育學生具備整合、表達、呈現研究成果與撰寫論文之能力。 Cultivate the students be capable of integrating, expressing, representing the research results and writing thesis. 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

A 船舶或機電系統工程的高階專業知識與創新之能力。

B 策劃、執行專題研究及呈現研究成果之能力。

D 創新思考及獨立解決問題的能力。


